@Node "INT" "Introduction"

@{b}@{u}Introduction@{uu}@{ub}

Executor consists of a selection list from which you can run up to 1000
programs (applications, utilities, tools, scripts, games) with a simple
double-click.


@Endnode
@Node "SYR" "System requirements"

@{b}@{u}System requirements@{uu}@{ub}

Executor requires Kickstart 2.04+, the diskfont.library in the LIBS: directory
and the AmigaDOS Execute command in the C: directory.


@Endnode
@Node "INS" "Installation"

@{b}@{u}Installation@{uu}@{ub}

To install Executor, simply drag its icon to any drawer of your choice.


@Endnode
